{{Top|canon=Berubium}}
A precious mineral, '''berubian''' was a frequent tool of con-artists who would "salt" a [[Mining/Legends|mine]], giving it the impression of having found a valuable cache of berubian. [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] was fooled by such a ruse in the [[Borgo asteroid belt]].

